title: Melodic Rock 4 the gym!
description:
Here's some songs of great great bands that will never be forgotten amongs the fans of the melodic rock genre. some new n some old. these tunes are excellent in the gym, at the party and in the bedroom!



Europe, Alias, Hardline, H.e.a.t, Enuff Z'nuff, Eclipse, Blue Tears, Tall Stories, Giant, Dare etc.



enjoy!

...and remember to stick to your guns, buy the albums if you like the songs and most important of all... Rock On!!! :)


(more torrents comin' up if there's a interest!)


/BeckisDreamer
